<a name="1055"></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Exhibitor Planning Webinar Archive Now Available</div>
<br />
<IMG height=51 hspace=8 src="/print/images/content/TechnologyEM.gif" width=150 align=right vspace=10>If you missed our "CES Chalk Talk" Webinar for exhibitors, <A href="http://content.ce.org/2009CESVideos/exhibitorWebinar/109118.wmv " target=_blank>download the free archive of the seminar</A>. Produced in conjunction with Tech-EM.com and Event Marketer magazine, this hour-long online seminar will get your tradeshow exhibit programs in shape for CES and beyond. Give us an hour and we'll arm you with CES changes and updates, exhibitor trends and case studies, design ideas and booth technologies, tips for increasing traffic and leads and more. <A href="http://content.ce.org/2009CESVideos/exhibitorWebinar/109118.wmv " target=_blank>Download here.</A>

